\vec F_r = k \frac{\vec r - \vec r_0}{ {\left| \vec r - \vec r_0 \right|}^3 } \cdot \hat r = k \frac{r - \frac{3a}{5} \left(  \sin \theta \cos \phi + \sin \theta \sin \phi - \cos \theta) \right)}{ {\left| \vec r - \vec r_0 \right|}^3 }
